{"tid":1434473,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"悲觀●分析●打氣po","createTime":"2019-08-08T19:34:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T00:31:12.000Z","uid":200179,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"982dfeaab080994b50e51d97abfd52780e483fc5","tid":1434473,"uid":200179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:34:59.000Z","msg":"用左成晚睇啲外國人對香港抗爭運動嘅comments<br />\n我淨係講笑鳩我地/唔理解我地嘅comment<br />\n(當然起碼有一大半係五毛/玩膠/誇張)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 佢地感受唔到我地嘅痛楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正如見到敘利亞打仗<br />\n我地可能會覺得啲抗爭者好慘<br />\n但係唔會sad到食唔落飯，瞓唔著覺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 其實勇武抗爭係無可避免<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有啲話我地唔係和平示威<br />\n因為佢地見到我地畀狗打之後用遮還擊/自衛<br />\n對佢地嚟講擋棍都係暴力<br />\n所以唔使執著和唔和平，會唔會太暴力，過左火<br />\n你點做都係會話你非和平<br />\n外國啲抗爭運動示威者會主動攻擊添<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有如果和平可以打勝仗14年就已經有真普選了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 佢地認為啲狗除左用實彈之外，都係使用適當武力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大部分講香港啲狗唔夠美國/法國殘忍<br />\n如果喺美國發生就點點點<br />\n殘忍嘅事實就係部分人唔care我地點樣俾狗不公平對待<br />\n<br />\n4. 笑我地用勁多遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔使理佢地，視覺上差啲姐<br />\n不如大家反問佢地有咩可以好過遮<br />\n再開個發達大計俾佢地<br />\n邊個諗到有野好過遮就賣果樣<br />\n我地用得開心，佢地賺得開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總之唔好打哂飛機話全世界睇住我地<br />\n唔忍心睇住我地俾極權打壓<br />\n我地嘅籌碼大部分同資金/錢有關，唔係同理心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n場仗一定要靠我地打埋落去<br />\n要智取同時要用武力對抗<br />\n唔捱落去有籌碼都冇用<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下開放討論<br />\n歡迎樂觀想法"},{"pid":"b3cebf898cdfd28eabade2cf3970142396c5e797","tid":1434473,"uid":200179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:38:15.000Z","msg":"好想快啲搞全港嘉年華<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺街度揮屬於香港人嘅旗<br />\nparty all night<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7d83092c6393030d8219ba9af2480655b6e7a80","tid":1434473,"uid":197716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:44:54.000Z","msg":"做有50% 唔做咩都冇"},{"pid":"fd0c3be63f9252a478f54493d58bb092c4bfd4a6","tid":1434473,"uid":200179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:45:12.000Z","msg":"好想每年七夕搞幻彩fing Hong Kong呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"415e86da06b9cef17347543aca2118f760136db2","tid":1434473,"uid":200179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7d83092c6393030d8219ba9af2480655b6e7a80","tid":1434473,"uid":197716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:44:54.000Z","msg":"做有50% 唔做咩都冇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:48:54.000Z","msg":"努力推高個%<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人考試咁叻<br />\n一定攞到滿分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f502f6e4e08e19efbbbb09f373235a2a684ec77","tid":1434473,"uid":166659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:56:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 8月9日和你飛 沙田黃大仙燒衣紙</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 8月10日和你飛 中環守護孩子 大埔遊行</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 8月11日 和你飛 大埔港島東遊行</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家記得推post不忘文宣啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[行動post 冇人理]未來數日反送中活動簡報<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1433511\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1433511</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2b7db3bb6330ca6701745b943a0323e5996fd4f7","tid":1434473,"uid":200179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T20:02:31.000Z","msg":"仲有唔好忘記世界各地都有示威活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好迫外國剩係留意香港<br />\n例如上個月moscow和平集會拉左600幾人<br />\n佢地都有冇警告下俾警察打傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果可以we connect其他被打壓/對民主有理想嘅外國同路人，會唔會有用？<br />\n喺國與國之間合作對抗，人地輸入武力知識，香港輸出金錢同建設知識<br />\n可能係其中一個以香港嘅長處幫到自己嘅方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57ec82e60743e27e62fedb69b0f07729ac3978a8","tid":1434473,"uid":200179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T20:10:14.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n撤惡法<br />\n銷控罪<br />\n非暴動<br />\n查警暴<br />\n真普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8RcSgwD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8RcSgwD.jpg&h=105914bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n希望大家唔好忘記有好多人已經付出左好多<br />\n停落嚟就會前功盡廢<br />\n我地冇一個選項叫「輸」<br />\n<br />\n我已經聞到烤肉味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時慶祝活動見"},{"pid":"8a7e6d3dfef62f6adedeb72cdcda35600a7d32d8","tid":1434473,"uid":200179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T20:19:44.000Z","msg":"可能有人睇咗幾個月抗爭日程表開始攰<br />\n但係我就好想快啲睇到慶祝日程表<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f021016704a9604514c78af54516b81a46c26749","tid":1434473,"uid":83902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T20:24:42.000Z","msg":"香港加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0250a1531045e519987111848ab3e05748608a0f","tid":1434473,"uid":200179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T21:16:13.000Z","msg":"有冇人想俾我打個氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef9cc88f992b4f82fec4303d901eef9bfcde1bd","tid":1434473,"uid":200179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T22:21:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37e2fd150cd647100c9c860e96f30ba003b0ebd7","tid":1434473,"uid":200179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:31:12.000Z","msg":"今日聽講有大明星返香港<br />\n大家一齊去接機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}